    • putComment

      public void putComment​(java.lang.String sectionName, java.lang.String key, java.lang.String comment)
      Description copied from interface: IIniConfig
      Adds the comment to the specified item in the section.

      If the section is null, the comment is used as a header for the whole ini configuration. If the key is null, the comment is used as a header for the specified section. If both the section and the key are null, than the comment is used as the header for the whole ini configuration.

      Specified by:
      putComment in interface IIniConfig
